    <title>LaTeX特殊矩阵的排版</title>
    <url>/2020/04/24/LaTeX%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%92%E7%89%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="blkarray"><a href="#blkarray" class="headerlink" title="blkarray"></a>blkarray</h1><p>利用blkarray宏包提供的blockarray环境及其子环境block排版上方和左侧带有数字标记的矩阵。<br><figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;blockarray&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;ccccccc&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">&amp; 1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;block&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;c[cccccc]&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    1 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    2 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    3 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    4 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    5 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    6 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;block&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;blockarray&#125;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><img src="/assets/LaTeX特殊矩阵的排版/matrix_1.png" alt="上方和左侧带数字标记"></p>
<p>利用blkarray宏包提供的blockarray环境及其子环境block排版上方和右侧带有数字标记的矩阵。<br><figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;blockarray&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;ccccccc&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6 &amp; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;block&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;[cccccc]c&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 2 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 3 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 4 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 5 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 6 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;block&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;blockarray&#125;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><img src="/assets/LaTeX特殊矩阵的排版/matrix_2.png" alt="上方和右侧带数字标记"></p>
<p>利用blkarray宏包提供的blockarray环境及其子环境block排版下方和左侧带有数字标记的矩阵。<br><figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;blockarray&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;ccccccc&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;block&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;c[cccccc]&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 2 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 3 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 4 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 5 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 6 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;block&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    &amp; 1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;blockarray&#125;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><img src="/assets/LaTeX特殊矩阵的排版/matrix_3.png" alt="下方和左侧带数字标记"></p>
<p>利用blkarray宏包提供的blockarray环境及其子环境block排版下方和右侧带有数字标记的矩阵。<br><figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;blockarray&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;ccccccc&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;block&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;[cccccc]c&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 2 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 3 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 4 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 5 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 6 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;block&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6 &amp; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;blockarray&#125;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><img src="/assets/LaTeX特殊矩阵的排版/matrix_4.png" alt="下方和右侧带数字标记"></p>
]]></content>
